{"tid":2057440,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果本土贏哂立法會初選=泛民已成歷史","createTime":"2020-06-09T11:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T16:10:19.000Z","uid":324193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8326eaa4be93b476a02ef036e813babb2b612ed6","tid":2057440,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:14:03.000Z","msg":"//初選另一焦點是泛本土派（包含自決派、港獨派、素人）能在跟傳統泛民的對決中，贏得多少個席位。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果在六四晚會中的港獨口號已經蓋過「平反六四」的聲音，這些聲音入面有多少可以轉化為對泛本土派的實質支持，願意在選舉中投他們一票。泛本土派跟泛民的背後的意識形態，實際是港獨與一國兩制之爭，香港本位和大中華思想的對決。</span>市民是否承認一國兩制失敗、是否依然相信理想中一國兩制能夠成功、是否對港獨持更開放的態度，以上問題都可以在初選結果中看出端倪。如果是泛本土派勝，則泛民必須調整其論述，免於日後被淘汰。如果是泛民勝，則泛本土派要發展一翼較溫和的本土主義，以吸納泛民支持者。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSWjGyn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSWjGyn.jpg&h=c546b6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwqAeTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwqAeTo.jpg&h=13f3c137&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lu7bxE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLu7bxE4.jpg&h=813c3342&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jLSSg6L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjLSSg6L.jpg&h=96f88b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立評論人要你like and share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112157957141912/posts/136725201351854/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112157957141912%2Fposts%2F136725201351854%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=acfd59e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112157957141912/posts/136725201351854/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"31a564eee584b716d3a5f85355b1d175e30a523c","tid":2057440,"uid":10809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2623e747b2fa0473b7aadfd7d0d65d1831f1abec","tid":2057440,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"難啲<br />\n不過利益真係要再分配"},{"pid":"1bc0207445b5f0af5f7d8aceae5fc360dd2dfc3e","tid":2057440,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:02:00.000Z","msg":"71112 初選要大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074331&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=bfb50516\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074331&h=63d4622f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074331</a>"},{"pid":"d41b2572f113248bf9fbd0af4adff9c71c448857","tid":2057440,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"68b105bf13e051811193d2b09a8344a4998bd2eb","tid":2057440,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"702e913408bd9e86bd3c6ca6e0c49ad41fd67f51","tid":2057440,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:00:46.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"001614e770da1269ee7c1c1f859ca14589f01bd1","tid":2057440,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:10:19.000Z","msg":"自推4"}]}